gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 120, Suns 105
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Suns, 120-105. Domantas Sabonis recorded his 4th triple double this season (28 points, 11 rebounds, 11 assists) for the Kings, with DeAaron Fox adding 23 points and seven assists in the victory. Kevin Durant tallied 28 points and seven rebounds for the Suns in the losing effort. The Kings improve to 17-10 in the regular season, while the Suns fall to 14-14.
